        {
            "title": "據Sky News報導 前巴克萊銀行高管Kheraj入圍滙豐主席候選人名單",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> Sky News報導稱，前巴克萊高管Naguib Kheraj是滙豐控股主席杜嘉祺(Mark Tucker)潛在接班候選人之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Sky News周六報導，該行已將Kheraj列入下一任主席候選人入圍名單。Kheraj在巴克萊工作了十多年，擔任過集團財務總監和副主席。他還曾擔任JPMorgan Cazenove CEO和渣打銀行副主席。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5月意外宣布將要卸任的杜嘉祺，將從10月1日開始擔任友邦非執行主席。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Ex-Barclays Executive Kheraj in Running for HSBC Chair, Sky Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
